  "prompt": "What is the Dishwasher market share (players), size and forecast in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, I can provide a general overview related to the market for dishwashers in India. However, specific and detailed figures on the market share, size, and forecast can be more precise when sourced from the latest industry reports, market research firms, or publications by business analysts.\n\nDishwasher Market in India:\n1. **Market Share**:\n   - Bosch is among the leading brands in the Indian dishwasher market.\n   - Other notable players include Siemens, LG, IFB, and Samsung.\n   - Additionally, brands like Whirlpool and Godrej also have their presence in the market.\n\n2. **Market Size**:\n   - The dishwasher market in India, though historically small, has been growing steadily.\n   - The total market size was expected to be valued in hundreds of crores INR, showing consistent growth year-on-year.\n   - Growth factors include increasing consumer disposable income, changing lifestyles, and urbanization trends.\n\n3. **Forecast**:\n   - The market is forecasted to grow at a CAGR of approximately 10-15% over the next few years.\n   - This growth can be attributed to higher demand from urban households, expanding middle class, and the convenience provided by dishwashers.\n   - Post-pandemic trends emphasize cleanliness and household hygiene, further boosting market demand.\n\nThese insights reflect the broader trends observed up to the given period. For the latest and most accurate information, I recommend consulting recent market research reports from firms such as Nielsen, Statista, TechSci Research, or another reputable source specializing in appliance market analytics in India.",
